* {{Cite journal|year=1899|title=続日本紀を上る表の約解|url=https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/3364698/1/19|journal=國學院雜誌|volume=5|issue=9|pages=35 - 43|doi=10.11501/3364698}}
