* {{Cite journal|year=1899|title=続日本紀を上る表の約解（承前）|url=https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/3364700/1/29|journal=國學院雜誌|volume=5|issue=11|pages=54 - 62|doi=10.11501/3364700}}
* {{Cite journal|year=1899|title=続日本紀を上る表の約解（承前・完）|url=https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/3364701/1/16|journal=國學院雜誌|volume=5|issue=12|pages=29 - 37|doi=10.11501/3364701}}
* {{Cite journal|year=1900|title=文武天皇即位前紀約解|url=https://dl.ndl.go.jp/ja/pid/3364709/1/29|journal=國學院雜誌|volume=6|issue=6|pages=63 - 72|doi=10.11501/3364709}}
* {{Cite journal|year=1900|title=官曹事類考、天長格抄考|url=https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/3364710/1/34|journal=國學院雜誌|volume=6|issue=7|pages=65 - 72|doi=10.11501/3364710}}

